N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4011.3 - Prerequisites

State Regulations

In order to win a daily double, it is necessary for
the purchaser of a daily double ticket to select the winners of each of the two
races specified for the daily double. If either of his or her selections fails
to win, his or her contract is voided, except as hereinafter
provided. Notes
